# EcoFeast 2.0 — Project Overview

**EcoFeast** is an autonomous, multi-agent food-rescue orchestration system built on top of Django. It integrates classical Machine Learning (XGBoost + SHAP), GenAI (Llama 3/4 via Groq), RAG (SentenceTransformers + Qdrant), and Agentic AI (LangGraph orchestrator) to coordinate food redistribution from donors to NGOs.

---

## 🏗️ Technical Architecture

The following diagram illustrates the flow of a donation request from intake to fulfillment, highlighting the interactions between different layers and agent modules:

```mermaid
graph TD
    %% Entry points
    Donor[Donor User] -->|1. Image upload / Chat text / Manual Form| Django[Django Backend API]
    
    %% GenAI / ML Intake
    Django -->|2. Route to Appopriate Service| IntakeRoute{Intake Router}
    IntakeRoute -->|Vision Upload| VisionSvc[GenAI Service: Vision Intake<br/>Llama Vision via Groq]
    IntakeRoute -->|Free-text description| ChatSvc[GenAI Service: Chat Intake<br/>Llama 3.3 70B JSON mode]
    IntakeRoute -->|Form submission| MLPredictor[ML Service: XGBoost Predictor]
    
    VisionSvc -->|Auto-populate form| DonorConfirm[Donor Confirmation]
    ChatSvc -->|Auto-populate form| DonorConfirm
    DonorConfirm -->|Submit| MLPredictor
    
    %% ML Pipeline
    MLPredictor -->|Extract features via FeatureBuilder| XGB[XGBoost Model]
    MLPredictor -->|Analyze features| SHAP[SHAP Explainer]
    SHAP -->|SHAP contributions| LlamaExplain[GenAI Explainer<br/>SHAP to text via LLM]
    
    %% LangGraph Orchestration
    LlamaExplain -->|3. Trigger agent pipeline| Orchestrator[LangGraph Orchestrator]
    
    subgraph LangGraph StateMachine [LangGraph Orchestrator]
        IntakeAgent[Intake Agent<br/>Collects & normalizes data]
        VerifyAgent[Verification Agent<br/>Performs anomaly detection]
        MatchAgent[Matching Agent<br/>Invokes RAG matcher]
        LogisticsAgent[Logistics Agent<br/>Coordinates claims & escalations]
        
        IntakeAgent --> VerifyAgent
        VerifyAgent -->|Valid?| MatchAgent
        VerifyAgent -->|Invalid| EndFailed[End: Run Failed]
        MatchAgent --> LogisticsAgent
        LogisticsAgent -->|Accepted?| EndSuccess[End: Run Completed]
        LogisticsAgent -->|Timeout / Rejected?| LogisticsAgent
    end
    
    %% RAG Service
    MatchAgent -->|4. Request candidates| RAGMatcher[RAG Service: NGO Matcher]
    RAGMatcher -->|Cosine similarity search| Qdrant[(Qdrant Vector DB)]
    RAGMatcher -->|Weighted re-ranking| RAGRank[Combined Score:<br/>Semantic match + Distance + Capacity + Reliability]
    RAGRank -->|Ranked list of NGOs| MatchAgent
    
    %% Qdrant Sync
    NGOAdmin[NGO Capability Doc] -->|Embed via SentenceTransformers| Qdrant
    
    %% DB & Frontend
    Orchestrator -->|5. Save execution results| AgentRunDB[(PostgreSQL Database)]
    AgentRunDB -->|6. Query status / logs| Observability[Observability Dashboard<br/>Django + Chart.js]
```

